00:05:24.090 --> 00:05:25.900
Hadi, gidelim.

00:05:25.900 --> 00:05:27.150
Evet!

00:05:27.150 --> 00:05:29.010
Hinata, tuvalete gitmen gerekiyor mu?

00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:31.750
